    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to my blog! This is my first post using Hexo and Fluid theme.</p><h2 id="About-this-blog"><a href="#About-this-blog" class="headerlink" title="About this blog"></a>About this blog</h2><p>This is a personal blog where I’ll share my thoughts, experiences, and technical knowledge. I’m excited to start this journey and hope you’ll find something interesting here.</p><h2 id="Features"><a href="#Features" class="headerlink" title="Features"></a>Features</h2><ul><li>Beautiful and responsive design</li><li>Dark mode support</li><li>Reading progress indicator</li><li>Code highlighting</li><li>Image lightbox</li><li>Math formula support</li><li>And many more!</li></ul><h2 id="Getting-started"><a href="#Getting-started" class="headerlink" title="Getting started"></a>Getting started</h2><p>To create a new post, run:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Your Post Title&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>To start the development server:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Happy blogging! 🎉</p>]]></content>
    
    
